videos.headline: Brown's big run sets up Ford's TD for Penn State
videos.description: Penn State's Journey Brown goes 85 yards to the Pitt 12, then a few plays later Devyn Ford walks into the end zone for the 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown's big run sets up Ford's TD for Penn State) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: Davis gives Pitt the lead with 3-yard TD
videos.description: Pitt running back Vincent Davis is spun into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Davis gives Pitt the lead with 3-yard TD) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: Penn State kicker nails school-record 57-yard FG
videos.description: Penn State kicker Jordan Stout nails a school-record 57-yard field goal to tie the game right before the half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Penn State kicker nails school-record 57-yard FG) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: Pitt's Taysir Mack makes incredible catch at the 1
videos.description: Pitt wide receiver Taysir Mack goes up with the defender and makes a phenomenal catch at the 1-yardline.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pitt's Taysir Mack makes incredible catch at the 1) 2019/09/14

videos.headline: Narduzzi: We're trying to win, not go to OT
videos.description: Pitt head coach Pat Narduzzi defends his decision to kick a field goal instead of going for it on 4th down because they wanted to win and they knew two scores was the goal.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Narduzzi: We’re trying to win, not go to OT) 2019/09/14
